The fruit_processor gem works with fortranxunit on sourceforge

To generate and install gem:
rake install

(Possibly you need sudo as
  sudo rake install
)

To install existing gem:
gem install pkg/fruit_processor-(version number).gem



-------------------------------------------
Issue on some versions of ruby and minitest
-------------------------------------------
On some versions of ruby (between version 1.9 and 2.1) and minitest (version 5),
  test/fruit_processor_test.rb
may need modification.
A sample of modification is
  test/fruit_processor_test_ruby2.rb
See
  https://sourceforge.net/p/fortranxunit/bugs/5/

